Author: UnusualReport
Text: I had this idea that I should live on Russian rye bread and yogurt so I went on a 4 hour round trip to go to a Russian bakery.  Later I realized the bakery accepts order by phone.

Author: LolitaJane
Text: I once went binge food shopping, realized my wallet was at home, and I walked around in the grocery store filling my cloth grocery bag completely nonchalantly, and then just wandered out.  No one stopped me.  Felt bad about it later but also kind of shocked?
